The paper deals with the semantics and implementation of logic programming, specifically coinductive definitions and their relation to coalgebra. This makes it likely to belong to the sub-categories of Logic in Computer Science (cs.LO), Programming Languages (cs.PL), Software Engineering (cs.SE), Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS), and Machine Learning (cs.LG) which deal with similar topics.
